    "## Notes on the property functions\n",
    "\n",
    "The property correlations below are simplified on purpose.  \n",
    "They are not intended to be a full thermodynamic package. They are only meant to provide the values needed for the DCMD design model.\n",
    "\n",
    "The main functions are:\n",
    "\n",
    "- `density(w, T)` for brine density\n",
    "- `cp_solution(w, T)` for brine heat capacity\n",
    "- `boiling_point_elevation(w, T_P)` for the threshold temperature difference\n",
    "- `hvap(T)` for latent heat of vaporisation\n",
    "- `hL(w, T)` for liquid enthalpy by simple numerical integration\n",
    "\n",
    "These are the functions the DCMD model calls repeatedly in each segment."
   ]
