    "## Notes on the system wrapper and the output tables\n",
    "\n",
    "The `MDSinglePass` class is only a thin wrapper around the DCMD model.  \n",
    "Its job is to:\n",
    "\n",
    "- prepare the feed basis\n",
    "- call the DCMD solver\n",
    "- convert the main outputs into engineering units used in the V2 report\n",
    "- build cleaner output tables for checking\n",
    "\n",
    "The last code cell runs the model once and prints:\n",
    "1. a short summary of the overall MD result\n",
    "2. a thermal table for all 50 segments\n",
    "3. a mass/flux table for all 50 segments\n",
    "\n",
    "It also writes the CSV files so the same numbers can be uploaded to GitHub with the notebook."
   ]
